<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-PMU_B08.html">PMU_B08</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>An event B08 indicates that a certificate/permission for a health professional is revoked.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The EVN segment is used to indicate the effective or planned date.</p>
</div>
